GetMaxBorrow().details: max borrowable amount from vault, will also impact utilization rate of lending protocol

acceptOwnership().details: The new owner accepts the ownership transfer.

borrowLeverage(uint256,bool).details: called from CNumaToken leverage function borrow from vault to deposit as collateral

buy(uint256,uint256,address).details: Buy numa from token (token approval needed)

extractRewards().details: transfers rewards to rwd_address and updates reference price

getBuyNumaAmountIn(uint256).details: Estimate number of tokens needed to get an amount of numa no need to simulate rwd extraction as extractrewards is called when borrowing from vault

getBuyNumaSimulateExtract(uint256).details: Estimate number of Numas from an amount of token with extraction simulation

getEthBalance().details: vaults' balance in Eth including debt

getSellNumaAmountIn(uint256).details: Estimate number of numas needed to get an amount of token no need to simulate rwd extraction as extractrewards is called when borrowing from vault

getSellNumaSimulateExtract(uint256).details: Estimate number of tokens from an amount of numa with extraction simulation

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

pauseBuy(bool).details: unpause buying and selling from vault

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

pendingOwner().details: Returns the address of the pending owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

repayLeverage(bool).details: called from CNumaToken leverage function repay to vault using borrowed amount from CNumaToken (converted to collateral token)

rewardsValue().details: returns the estimated rewards value of lst token

sell(uint256,uint256,address).details: Sell numa (burn) to token (numa approval needed)

setCTokens(address,address).details: set the IVaultOracle address (used to compute token price in Eth)

setFeeWhitelist(address,bool).details: adds an address as fee whitelisted

setMinLiquidationsPc(uint256).details: adds an address as fee whitelisted

setOracle(address).details: set the IVaultOracle address (used to compute token price in Eth)

setVaultManager(address).details: set the IVaultManager address (used to total Eth balance of all vaults)

transferOwnership(address).details: Starts the ownership transfer of the contract to a new account. Replaces the pending transfer if there is one. Can only be called by the current owner.
